g to TNT Sports after the game, Emery said his team controlled the game, but were not clinical.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.277191017564826e-22, \"text\": \"TNT Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\", \"score\": 0.9999999983610905, \"rank\": 1.6388297787064391e-09, \"text\": \"Emery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We got to be in Europe at the end of last season and this year we enjoyed it, but to win is very difficult and we are in the process [of developing],\\\" Emery said.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"last season\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"Emery\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They [Olympiakos] deserve to be in the final.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympiakos\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We lost it in the first 90 minutes at home and we were not competitive.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first 90 minutes\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We started this first half well, they scored but we controlled the game, but we were not clinical.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this first half\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is an experience for us at Aston Villa after a long time [of not being in Europe] and again we are going to compete in Europe next year.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an experience\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"Aston Villa\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course we are a little bit disappointed, a little bit frustrated but we have to move on quickly.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We started the first leg and maybe we were favourites but after the first leg, we were not.\\\"\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first leg\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"favourites\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"the first leg\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Transfer: 'They are pushing, he's top priority' - Romano names player Arsenal want to sign I am very calm - Vinicius Jr speaks on winning 2024 Ballon d'Or EPL: Wes Brown criticizes Sesko after Man Utd's 3-1 win over Aston Villa EPL: Man Utd seek revenge against Aston Villa in battle for Champions League spot EPL: Chris Sutton predicts Man Utd vs Aston Villa, Chelsea against Newcastle, others Paul Merson predicts Man Utd vs Aston Villa, Chelsea against Newcastle, others EPL: Paul Merson predicts